2022-04-13T16:12:53Z	(#o3cxqba) **Put my money where my mouth is!**‚Ä®‚Ä®As I've discussed previously (taken from the book 'Predictably irrational') money changes everything. From a favour now you have the obligation to keep lights on, and some predictability on how everything works.‚Ä®From a friend giving stuff for free, now you are a supplier. That's why free social networks are in that Uncanny valley of being free, but arguably you are the product. ‚Ä®‚Ä®It's an interesting experiment to charge for some part of the product (even being a non-profit). You'll see how people change. (And that's not bad, but part of self-sustainability)
